name: Anand Enterprises
overview:
Established in the year 1975, we, “Anand Enterprises, Pune”, are actively engaged in distributing a wide assortment of Laboratory Chemicals.

Quality Assurance: Ever since the foundation stone of our organization was laid, we are paying significant priority towards facilitating clients with a quality-proven assortment of Laboratory Chemicals offered by us.

Why Us: With our wide gamut of quality products, we have always been the first choice of our clients.

Our Team: Manned by a team of dexterous professionals, we have been able to attain a prominent stature in the countrywide market.

Infrastructure: We have a spacious state-of-the art-infrastructure and one of the largest manufacturing units in the country equipped with latest machinery and other equipments.

Brands, We Deal In: Over the period of time, we have been able to become the prime choice of patrons owing to the tremendous support of the brands that we deal in.
